去連儂牆貼文宣<br />\nIg fb 一齊 share 香港人既訴息傳播速度係最高 <br />\n幾日內 要全香港人知道星期一朝早有大鑊野！<br />\n<br />\n另外重申 11 11係開花 塞車塞鐵係當日既序幕！<br />\n<br />\n有好多人話太急 未ready 未夠時間 請問反抗要等幾耐？反抗就係即刻！仲想等幾多手足犧牲先行動？<br />\n<br />\n今次同工會罷工既性質係兩回事 我地係張抗爭日常化 星期一 當開花到全城癱瘓 係返唔到工 唔到你選擇罷唔罷！<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以再不斷係星期六日活動 星期一照舊返工既節奏到輪迴 咁既抗爭習慣 連抗爭都要有日程接表既話 注定比人睇死！<br />\n<br />\n星期一張會係推動革命巨輪 係真正既突破開始<br />\n11 /11 12 13 14⋯一路咁去 個社會持續癱瘓<br />\n唔駛一個禮拜 政府即刻跪低！<br />\n<br />\n大家記時先明白 真正核彈引爆個制係我地手上<br />\n<br />\n而11 11 就係核爆既開始！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"一切都係剛剛開始。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1e86850e1bce611a4e69db42fc125bb20ff1e5","tid":1699472,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fdb6fafdf9bc804fbac5929dcf6feb2c72bac0bf","tid":1699472,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b5c437d92d0b8f4b04f247e5f8ab3cbc43b0f6bd","tid":1699472,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-